gomodel:SYNGO_4034  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 7 C and D: immunoelectron microscopy demonstrate localisation of NPY on dense-core vesicles. (arrows mark the immunoreaction product, while DCVs are separately labelled)\n\nThe paper comments on specificity tests for the antibody used against NPY by staining it on WT and NPY KO mice. However, the data wasn't shown. The rabbit NPY antibody was produced referred from Gaikwad et al., 2005. (PMID: 20035453 ). Experimental description: male Sprague-Dawley were used" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
